  "About 52,500 kg": "",
  "For neutral buoyancy: total weight = buoyant force. F_b = 1025*9.8*6500 = 6.53e7 N. Ballast weight needed = 6.53e7 - 6.0e7 = 5.3e6 N = 541,000 kg. About 525,000 kg.": "",
  "A 10 cm x 10 cm x 10 cm cube of wood (density 800 kg/m^3) floats in water. A mass is placed on top, pushing the cube until it is fully submerged. What is the mass?": "",
